casebody.data:
Cincinnati Bar Association v. Wang.

[Cite as Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Wang (1991), 59 Ohio St. 3d 67.]

(No. 90-2534 Submitted February 13, 1991 Decided April 24, 1991.) *68Hollis A. Moore III and Richard J. Ruebel, for relator. John H. Burlew, for respondent. Per Curiam.

We concur in the board’s findings of misconduct and in its recommendation. Respondent is hereby publicly reprimanded. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
